{"tid":125431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳浩天選舉呈請法援上訴申請成功】","createTime":"2017-02-18T13:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T16:38:40.000Z","uid":26671,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e018b5d04aa64dc219904cd24c94964e0bdb6b3","tid":125431,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"民族黨召集人陳浩天昨日 (17/2) 接獲律師通知，其選舉呈請的法律援助申請上訴成功，將會獲批法援，進行就被選舉主任取消2016年立法會選舉參選資格而提出的選舉呈請。<br />\n<br />\n法律援助署月前於徵詢一名資深大律師的法律意見後，決定拒絕陳浩天的法援申請。然而，審理上訴的高等法院聆案官認為，按法援的審批準則，即是否有合理機會勝訴，陳浩天的選舉呈請符合申請要求，故批准陳浩天的上訴。<br />\n<br />\n敝黨歡迎法院裁決，會繼續進行選舉呈請，以不斷擴大殖民政府的憲制危機，並努力推動香港民族運動，務必令殖民政府威權殆盡，節節敗退，永不翻身。"},{"pid":"8eb6f2e8c4d45af0807bb5d622481da0c12d0c59","tid":125431,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb57c86100b0ff1114c51a53d00d5fdc061906ee","tid":125431,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6a60ed9acfd5d4f46e6795ef11bc4ae3926f07","tid":125431,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8302bd4147ce6536142e60dcbbb1bccc96d1de1","tid":125431,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"窮撚搞港獨好處就係可以用政府錢告政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6144bfe556210a2ead4ed7e34884599bc5d40bbd","tid":125431,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮撚搞港獨好處就係可以用政府錢告政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass